Winx Club: Bloomix - Season 6 - Episode 11 (WEB-DL - 720p)

Get ready for more magical adventures with the Winx Club in these 13 enchanted
episodes from season 6! Join Bloom, Stella, Flora, Tecna, Aisha and Musa as they

new witch, Selina, trouble begins brewing. Selina sends evil Treants to attack

At the same time, Selina is sending Sphinx and Fire Eaters to attack! Can the Winx
put a stop to Selina and defeat the endless evil she is sending their way?
Don't miss this exciting season full of magic, friendship, courage and more!

Produced by Rainbow S.r.l. and Nickelodeon Studios.
